{"data":[{"text":"Claudeのチャット・Cowork・Codeの違い、しっかり整理してみた。\n\n結論から言うと、この3つは「難易度と自動化の深さ」で段階が分かれている。\n\nまずチャットモード。 https://t.co/YdQw1U6lzH","entities":{"urls":[{"start":89,"end":112,"url":"https://t.co/YdQw1U6lzH","expanded_url":"https://x.com/keitowebai/status/2037499356644094369/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/YdQw1U6lzH","media_key":"3_2037499348456701952"},{"start":89,"end":112,"url":"https://t.co/YdQw1U6lzH","expanded_url":"https://x.com/keitowebai/status/2037499356644094369/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/YdQw1U6lzH","media_key":"3_2037499350528798721"},{"start":89,"end":112,"url":"https://t.co/YdQw1U6lzH","expanded_url":"https://x.com/keitowebai/status/2037499356644094369/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/YdQw1U6lzH","media_key":"3_2037499352667873280"},{"start":89,"end":112,"url":"https://t.co/YdQw1U6lzH","expanded_url":"https://x.com/keitowebai/status/2037499356644094369/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/YdQw1U6lzH","media_key":"3_2037499354681122816"}]},"id":"2037499356644094369","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":22,"reply_count":6,"like_count":343,"quote_count":7,"bookmark_count":404,"impression_count":43202},"created_at":"2026-03-27T11:57:56.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037499356644094369"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"Claudeスキルを作ったら、必ず！\n検証用エージェントを含めましょう。\n必須！","id":"2037188904710004748","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":7,"reply_count":1,"like_count":139,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":91,"impression_count":12269},"created_at":"2026-03-26T15:24:18.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037188904710004748"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"Claude Codeのスキル作りにハマってる。どこかで伸びたら１つずつ動画にする。 https://t.co/RCGl1dmACZ","entities":{"urls":[{"start":43,"end":66,"url":"https://t.co/RCGl1dmACZ","expanded_url":"https://x.com/keitowebai/status/2037112748887466288/video/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/RCGl1dmACZ","media_key":"13_2037112391247523840"}]},"id":"2037112748887466288","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":5,"reply_count":3,"like_count":129,"quote_count":1,"bookmark_count":80,"impression_count":13720},"created_at":"2026-03-26T10:21:41.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037112748887466288"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"これで良いやん https://t.co/Cm5hfNBKYs","entities":{"urls":[{"start":8,"end":31,"url":"https://t.co/Cm5hfNBKYs","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/capcutapp/status/2036943209956344181","display_url":"x.com/capcutapp/stat…"}]},"id":"2037070780887163331","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":1,"like_count":32,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":28,"impression_count":10163},"created_at":"2026-03-26T07:34:55.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2037070780887163331"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"AI活用のコツ\nChatGPTは裏側でPythonを実行できます。つまり、「Pythonでできることは大体できるじゃね？」と捉えると、活用の発想が一気に広がります。Claudeも同じです。「スクリーンショットを撮りながら操作している」と理解した瞬間、できることのイメージが一気に湧いてきます。","id":"2036817723616047177","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":1,"reply_count":2,"like_count":62,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":18,"impression_count":7186},"created_at":"2026-03-25T14:49:22.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036817723616047177"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"Claude CoworkのComputer Use機能、実際に3つの使い方を検証してみた。\n\nカーソルとキーボードを丸ごとAIに渡す。APIもMCPも不要。パソコン上のあらゆるアプリを人間と同じように操作できる。\n\n↓具体的な活用法をスレッドで紹介する。","id":"2036766750696669237","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":6,"reply_count":4,"like_count":140,"quote_count":2,"bookmark_count":189,"impression_count":35138},"created_at":"2026-03-25T11:26:49.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036766750696669237"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"妻「子供ら風呂入れてー！」\n俺「ちょっと待って。AIに仕事の依頼だけさせて！」\n\nリアルにこの会話が最近おきてる。","id":"2036746750351081837","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":3,"reply_count":16,"like_count":135,"quote_count":8,"bookmark_count":6,"impression_count":18409},"created_at":"2026-03-25T10:07:20.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036746750351081837"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"Claude関連の研修や導入アドバイスのお問い合わせが、一気に増えてきました。まさに今が動くタイミングだと感じています。さらに、大手出版社の大型シリーズでの出版も決定し、Claudeへの注目度の高まりを実感。","id":"2036737438664757311","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":3,"reply_count":1,"like_count":47,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":5,"impression_count":4464},"created_at":"2026-03-25T09:30:20.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036737438664757311"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"今から色々育ててくる！ https://t.co/G7Y0erPaXh","entities":{"urls":[{"start":12,"end":35,"url":"https://t.co/G7Y0erPaXh","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/poke_times/status/2036442915837231298","display_url":"x.com/poke_times/sta…"}]},"id":"2036682184745189747","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":0,"reply_count":0,"like_count":5,"quote_count":0,"bookmark_count":0,"impression_count":3613},"created_at":"2026-03-25T05:50:47.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036682184745189747"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"},{"text":"Claude Code基礎講座\n導入後の便利機能準備＋スキル作成\n\nこちらの記事が非常に好評だったため、その内容をもとにオンラインセミナーを開催します。\n\n本セミナーでは、スキル作成の実演に加え、参加者の皆さまにも実際に一つスキルを作成していただくハンズオン形式で進めていきます。\n\n参加は以下から https://t.co/x5SS9YOcWi https://t.co/dnRFexkWH9","entities":{"urls":[{"start":150,"end":173,"url":"https://t.co/x5SS9YOcWi","expanded_url":"https://x.com/keitowebai/status/2036640148864254174/photo/1","display_url":"pic.x.com/x5SS9YOcWi","media_key":"3_2036640132498096128"},{"start":174,"end":197,"url":"https://t.co/dnRFexkWH9","expanded_url":"https://twitter.com/keitowebai/status/2035716807257108856","display_url":"x.com/keitowebai/sta…"}]},"id":"2036640148864254174","public_metrics":{"retweet_count":4,"reply_count":1,"like_count":35,"quote_count":2,"bookmark_count":32,"impression_count":18208},"created_at":"2026-03-25T03:03:45.000Z","edit_history_tweet_ids":["2036640148864254174"],"author_id":"1622624776337633280"}],"includes":{"users":[{"name":"KEITO\uD83D\uDCBBAIディレクター","public_metrics":{"followers_count":42088,"following_count":811,"tweet_count":9601,"listed_count":761,"like_count":9213,"media_count":2369},"id":"1622624776337633280","username":"keitowebai"}]},"meta":{"newest_id":"20374993566440943